1.25 cups almond milk
2 Tbsp almond butter
2 Tbsp maple syrup
1 tsp ground cinnamon
.5 tsp ground cardamom
.125 tsp salt
2 Cups Cauliflower rice
1.5 Tbsp raisins/currants
1 apple, coarsely chopped
.125 tsp almond extract

Add milk to pan and whisk in almond butter and maple syrup.
Add cinnamon, cardamom, and salt and whisk well.
Add cauli and raisins, bring to simmer until cauliflower is soft.
Add the apple and almond and cook for about a minute.
